<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1. Aw Thagau Thiengtho, hung inla,
 Ka thau hung hihhat in;
 Ka ginnau in ei muhsak in,
 * Zie gam nuom tak mai chuh. (2)

[V2]
 2. Gamthip gamgaw taihsan ing ka,
 Nat gam leh gimum gam;
 Nunkhuo-nawpna ah chieh ing-ka,
 * Kumkhuo nawpna achun. (2)

[V3]
 3. Kulhpi bulah ka um zing a,
 Ni eng hung suok ngakin;
 Ni lopi hung suok leh ka nuom,
 * Kalvari zawhna ni. (2)

[V4]
 4. Khawvel ah kipahna kim lo,
 A nawpna le a tawp;
 Kumsawt kipahna dang umlo,
 * Lal Isu pak loh ngal. (2)

[V5]
 5. A thagau uh Nang na pui a,
 Malai mithiengtho le;
 Kei le ka banin ei kai in,
 * Hin lamah ei pui in. (2)

[V6]
 6. Gamgaw gam hi hawhpai dingin,
 Gim um tamtak a um;
 Nang hatlo lungmuonpa Na hi,
 * Puipa hat le Na hi. (2)

[V7]
 7. Nangin mi na puih takphawt chuh,
 Pathien chate ahiu;
 Lampi lauhum ah ei puiin,
 * Lungsietna thagui in. (2)</lyrics>
<title>COME HOLY SPIRIT</title>
<hymn_number>210</hymn_number>
</song>